{"tid":1839506,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［幫我推上熱門］ 集思廣益如何順利進行醫護大罷工","createTime":"2020-01-24T12:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T15:07:58.000Z","uid":112185,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c90f6e0b627d600d475b5ea8906fced765ca8f","tid":1839506,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"醫護大罷工有<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">一大難處</span></ins>，就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">院內病人無人照顧，同埋有跟開既病人</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">首先提出要求</span></span></strong>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>如果政府於限期內無法完成</ins></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即啟動罷工程序</span></span></strong>。例如進行入境管制並提高透明度。<br />\n<br />\n假如政府於限期內不作出合理回應<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">定出明確罷工日</span></strong></span>，並開始<span style=\"color: brown;\">拒收新症</span>， 急症室維持有限度服務， <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">拒絕為發燒病人提供服務。 發燒及上呼吸道感染病人絕不上房，</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />並盡量安排病人出院， 減少於醫院內病人人數。</span></strong></span> 為罷工日受影響以預約之病人重新排期。<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">於罷工日安排最少量人手維持病房運作</span></span>， 確保病房內病人安全。 暫停急症室及專科門診服務。<br />\n<br />\n4. 通知消防員及其他相關救護團隊於<span style=\"color: orange;\">各區私家醫院取得急症服務</span>。<br />\n<br />\n5. 罷工日後短暫復工， 處理院內病人事務，繼續維持急症室內有限度服務。再定出限期要求政府回應訴求，如政府不作出合理回應，將展開長達一星期之罷工行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未諗到之後點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>大家有建議，更改同有補充歡迎提出，我會pin 大家有共職最update既plan。</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda280c726556d5c6c6ddd4b9f1609881056a33a","tid":1839506,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8c90f6e0b627d600d475b5ea8906fced765ca8f","tid":1839506,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"醫護大罷工有<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">一大難處</span></ins>，就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">院內病人無人照顧，同埋有跟開既病人</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">首先提出要求</span></span></strong>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>如果政府於限期內無法完成</ins></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即啟動罷工程序</span></span></strong>。例如進行入境管制並提高透明度。<br />\n<br />\n假如政府於限期內不作出合理回應<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">定出明確罷工日</span></strong></span>，並開始<span style=\"color: brown;\">拒收新症</span>， 急症室維持有限度服務， <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">拒絕為發燒病人提供服務。 發燒及上呼吸道感染病人絕不上房，</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />並盡量安排病人出院， 減少於醫院內病人人數。</span></strong></span> 為罷工日受影響以預約之病人重新排期。<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">於罷工日安排最少量人手維持病